                      Text hangs from the lines.</seg>
                           </layout>
                        </layoutDesc>
                     </objectDesc>
                
                     <handDesc>
                        <handNote scope="major" xml:id="hand-2">
                           <p>The upper text was copied by Hand B, in an upright <term type="script">minuscule</term> script, 
                    in brown ink, with minimal variation in letter size.
                    Ligatures and abbreviations for <hi rend="italic">nomina sacra</hi> are present.</p>
                           <p>
                              <hi rend="italic">Kappa, lambda</hi> and <hi rend="italic">ny</hi> are frequently in majuscule.
                  Syllabic abbreviations appear througout the line. Breathings and accents are round and 
                    not ligated. Mute <hi rend="italic">iota</hi> is absent.</p>
                           <p>Punctuation used includes the upper point and full stop.</p>
                        </handNote>
                     </handDesc>

                  </physDesc>

